Use of tobacco products in any vehicles or property owned by or under the control of the Burke Center for Youth is prohibited. Employees, if transporting residents in their private vehicle, may not use tobacco products in any form while in the presence of a child. Tobacco use of any kind by employees is prohibited at Pathfinders Ranch property. 

